# Qarint Games - Core Development Rules

## Cultural Safety & Values (STRICT)
- ALL generated dummy data, vocabulary, UI text, and scenarios MUST be safe and age-appropriate for children
- Examples: honesty, respecting parents, helping elders, sharing, kindness
- NO inappropriate, violent, or culturally insensitive content
- When filtering content, always prioritize family values and child safety

## Curriculum Base
- Use Cambridge YLE (Pre A1 Starters, A1 Movers, A2 Flyers) standard for vocabulary difficulty
- All vocabulary must be age-appropriate for children 4-12 years old

## UI/UX Design System (STRICT ADHERENCE)

### Sidebar
- Minimalist, light gray/white background
- Active state (e.g., "Games") must have:
  - Subtle gray background
  - Pinkish-red text/icon color (#EF4444 or similar)

