### Assets
- Heroicons for UI elements
- OpenMoji (via CDN: jsDelivr) for all game illustrations
- Format: `https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/hfg-gmuend/openmoji/color/svg/{HEX_CODE}.svg`

## Mechanics & Accessibility

### Productive Failure (Slapstick)
- NEVER deduct points for wrong answers
- Trigger "slapstick" CSS animation (`animate-funny-shake`) on wrong answers
- Make failing fun and encourage retries
- Use exaggerated, funny shaking or bouncing effects

### Audio
- Automatically use `window.speechSynthesis` (Web Speech API) to read English words aloud
- Trigger on card click/interaction
- Use English (en-US) voice

## Technical Stack
- Next.js 14+ (App Router)
- TypeScript
- Tailwind CSS
- Zustand for state management
- Supabase for database and auth
- Framer Motion for animations (if needed)
- @dnd-kit/core for drag & drop

## Code Quality
- Use TypeScript strictly
- Follow Next.js App Router conventions
- Implement proper error handling
- Use Server Actions for database operations
- Implement Row Level Security (RLS) in Supabase

